These are the review questions for coming Wednesday's quiz:

a) Explain the difference between the program and the process

b) Explain different memory divisions of the process

c) Distinguish between process stack and heap

d) What is Process Control Block? Describe the different states of the Process Control Block.

e) What do you understand by Process Schedulers? Describe their functions.

f) What is Context Switch? Explain in details the procedure of Context Switch

g) Explain the difference between Zombie and Orphan process

h) Explain how process communication takes place. What are the advantages of Interprocess communications?

i) Explain the difference between shared memory and message passing systems.

j) Learn also about the creation of the process.
